==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Homonym
<hw>Hom"o*nym</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>homonyme</ets>. See <er>Homonymous</er>.]</ety> <def>A word having
the same sound as another, but differing from it in meaning; as the noun
<xex>bear</xex> and the verb <xex>bear</xex>.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>homonyme</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Homonymous</ent>⟦br⟧
